snippet.title: Marvel Entertainment
snippet.description: Marvel is committed to bringing great stories, characters, and experiences to fans all over the world. We strive to foster an inclusive, diverse, respectful, and safe environment for all of our fans, and we ask the same of our fan communities. As such, we reserve the right to take action including but not limited to hiding, deleting, blocking, and reporting any posts on this account or page. Please also be aware that Marvel does not accept or consider unsolicited idea submissions.
